                "game-obj": "Traits",
                "game-id": "25f5e8b7c967616d13c70b777337cfd3",
                "text": "The armor is pliable and doesn\u2019t hinder most actions. You don\u2019t apply its check penalty to Acrobatics or Athletics checks.",
